## Metrics and KPIs

### Team Performance Metrics
- **Velocity**: Story points completed per sprint
- **Burndown**: Progress toward sprint goals
- **Cycle Time**: Time from story start to completion
- **Lead Time**: Time from story creation to completion
- **Throughput**: Number of stories completed per sprint

### Quality Metrics
- **Bug Rate**: Number of bugs per story
- **Test Coverage**: Percentage of code covered by tests
- **Code Review Coverage**: Percentage of code reviewed
- **Deployment Success Rate**: Percentage of successful deployments
- **Mean Time to Recovery**: Time to recover from failures

### Process Metrics
- **Sprint Goal Achievement**: Percentage of sprint goals met
- **Story Completion Rate**: Percentage of stories completed
- **Blocked Story Rate**: Percentage of stories blocked
- **Rework Rate**: Percentage of work that needs rework
- **Process Adherence**: Adherence to defined processes

### User Experience Metrics
- **User Satisfaction**: User feedback scores
- **Feature Adoption**: Percentage of users using new features
- **Performance Metrics**: Response times and throughput
- **Error Rates**: Application error rates
- **Support Tickets**: Number of support requests

