```

### Improvement Categories
- **Process Improvements**: Workflow and process enhancements
- **Tool Improvements**: Tool selection and configuration
- **Skill Improvements**: Team training and development
- **Communication Improvements**: Team communication enhancements
- **Quality Improvements**: Quality assurance enhancements

## Retrospective Facilitation

### Facilitation Guidelines
- **Neutral Facilitation**: Facilitator should be neutral
- **Equal Participation**: Ensure all team members participate
- **Time Management**: Keep retrospectives within time limits
- **Action Orientation**: Focus on actionable improvements
- **Follow-up**: Ensure action items are tracked and completed

### Facilitation Techniques
- **Round Robin**: Go around the room for input
- **Silent Writing**: Write thoughts before sharing
- **Dot Voting**: Vote on most important items
- **Affinity Mapping**: Group similar ideas
- **Timeboxing**: Set time limits for activities

